text: Deeply saddened to hear of the passing of the great man of God Billy Graham. His teachings have been a light to the world, and his legacy will be remembered as one of love, compassion, and godliness.

President Trump's State of the Union signaled his commitment to our great nation to combat terrorism, support our troops, grow our economy, and create opportunities to help every American realize the American dream. #SOTU
"As we rebuild America's strength and confidence at home, we are also restoring our strength and standing abroad." - @POTUS #SOTU

"As tax cuts create new jobs, let us invest in workforce development and job training. Let us open great vocational schools so our future workers can learn a craft and realize their full potential." - @POTUS #SOTU
"As we rebuild our industries, it is also time to rebuild our crumbling #infrastructure." - @POTUS #SOTU
"If you work hard, if you believe in yourself, if you believe in America, then you can dream anything, you can be anything, & together, we can achieve anything." - @POTUS #SOTU
"This April will be the last time you ever file under the old broken system -- and millions of Americans will have more take-home pay starting next month." - @POTUS #SOTU #TaxReformWorks
"Let us begin tonight by recognizing that the state of our Union is strong because our people are strong." - @POTUS #SOTU
President Trump will make his first State of the Union Address to Congress tonight. Will you be tuning in? What do you hope to hear @POTUS talk about during tonight's #SOTU?
This afternoon, the House will vote to appropriate $659.2B for a full year of funding for @DeptofDefense.
In-studio this morning w/ David Nelson on @wtif1075 to talk @POTUS support for rural America, impacts of #governmentshutdown on our military, 2018 legislative outlook in Congress. Tune in!

Republicans and @POTUS have been hard at work rebuilding our military, and the political games of @SenSchumer and @SenateDems are a detriment to the work we’ve done to provide for our troops, increase the size of our military, and protect our great nation.

Things a #governmentshutdown does:
1. Hurts our #Military 
2. Harms #NationalSecurity 
3. Strips low-income children of #healthcare 
4. Puts this country in jeopardy.
And yet, @SenateDems are still willing to vote NO.

Thousands of men & women all over our nation have answered the call to serve. A #SchumerShutdown:
1. Halts payment of more than 2M warfighters
2. Means 100K @USNationalGuard will be sent home from training
3. Halts pilot training
4. Cancels training for thousands of reservists
.@POTUS outlined a clear #NationalSecurityStrategy to protect Americans & the homeland, promote American prosperity, preserve peace through strength, & advance American influence. #NSS
I applaud @POTUS historic decision to recognize Jerusalem as Israel’s capital and relocate our embassy from Tel Aviv to Jerusalem, continuing the United States commitment to the Jewish people.

Retired Maj Gen Robert McMahon of Robins AFB was confirmed by U.S. Senate last night to be @DeptofDefense Assistant Sec. for Logistics & Materiel Readiness. I offer my congrats on behalf of Middle GA.

#FY18NDAA funds our nation’s military, addresses our readiness crisis, confronts aggression, addresses threats, rebuilds our military, protects force structure, & provides for our military families & warfighters.
